 2 SYSTEMPATH/Database/BaseConnection.php(652): CodeIgniter\Database\BaseConnection->simpleQuery('INSERT INTO `chapters` (`unit_id`, `name`, `slug`, `content`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES (\'1\', \'Generations Of Computers\', \'generations-of-computers\', \'<p class=\\"MsoNormal\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify;\\"><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">1940</span><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\"> में </span><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">&lsquo;Atanasoff Berry&rsquo;</span><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\"><span style=\\"mso-spacerun: yes;\\">&nbsp; </span>द्वारा पहले इलेक्&zwj;ट्रानिक कम्&zwj;प्&zwj;यूटर के विकास के बाद कम्&zwj;प्&zwj;यूटर ने इलेक्&zwj;ट्रानिक कम्&zwj;प्&zwj;यूटिंग के युग में कदम रखा। इलेक्&zwj;ट्रानिक कम्&zwj;प्&zwj;यूटर के विकास की शुरूआत </span><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">1946 </span><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">से मानी जाती है । &zwj;</span></p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"MsoNormal\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: .5in; line-height: normal;\\"><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">कम्&zwj;प्&zwj;यूटर की </span><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">Generation </span><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular