ge: EN-US;\\">अधिक तेज एवं विश्&zwj;वसनीय </span></p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo2;\\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\"><span style=\\"mso-list: Ignore;\\">&middot;<span style=\\"font: 7.0pt \\\'Times New Roman\\\';\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">प्रथम पीढ़ी की अपेक्षा कम खर्चीला</span></p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo2;\\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\"><span style=\\"mso-list: Ignore;\\">&middot;<span style=\\"font: 7.0pt \\\'Times New Roman\\\';\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">इसमे कोबोल एवं फार्ट्रान जैसी उच्&zwj;चस्&zwj;तीय प्रो्ग्रामिंग भाषाओं का विकास</span></p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\\"><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"MsoNormal\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\\"><strong><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; color: #4f81bd; mso-themecolor: accent1; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">कम्&zwj;प्&zwj;यूटर की तृतीय पीढ़ी (</span></strong><strong><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; color: #4f81bd; mso-themecolor: accent1; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">1964-1971</span></strong><strong><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; color: #4f81bd; mso-themecolor: accent1; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">)</span></strong><strong><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; color: #4f81bd; mso-themecolor: accent1; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\"> :-</span></strong></p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"MsoNormal\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\\"><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\"><span style=\\"mso-tab-count: 1;\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">कम्&zwj;प्&zwj;यूटरों की तृतीय पीढ़ी की शुरूआत </span><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">1964 </span><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">में हुई । इस पीढ़ी के <span style=\\"mso-spacerun: yes;\\">&nbsp;</span>कम्&zwj;प्&zwj;यूटरों में आई</span><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">.</span><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">सी. (इन्&zwj;ट्रीग्रेटेड सर्किट) का प्रयोग किया गया &zwj;। आई</span><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">.</span><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">सी. का अविष्&zwj;कार (टेक्&zwj;सास इन्&zwj;स्&zwj;टूमेंट कंपनी) के एक साइटिस्&zwj;ट जैक किल्&zwj;वी ने किया था। इस पीढ़ी के कम्&zwj;प्&zwj;यूटरों में आई.सी.एल. </span><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">2903, </span><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">आई.सी.एल </span><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">1900,</span><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\"> यूनिवैक&zwj; </span><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">1108 </span><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">और सिस्&zwj;टम </span><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">1360 </span><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">प्रमुख थे।</span></p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"MsoNormal\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\\"><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"MsoNormal\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\\"><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\"><span style=\\"mso-spacerun: yes;\\">&nbsp;</span></span><strong><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; color: #4f81bd; mso-themecolor: accent1; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">तृतीय पीढ़ी के कम्&zwj;प्&zwj;यूटरों के लक्षण </span></strong><strong><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; color: #4f81bd; mso-themecolor: accent1; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">&ndash;</span></strong></p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo3;\\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\"><span style=\\"mso-list: Ignore;\\">&middot;<span style=\\"font: 7.0pt \\\'Times New Roman\\\';\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">इन्&zwj;ट्रीग्रेटेड चिप का प्रयोग</span></p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo3;\\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\"><span style=\\"mso-list: Ignore;\\">&middot;<span style=\\"font: 7.0pt \\\'Times New Roman\\\';\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">प्रथम एवं द्वितीय पीढियों की अपेक्षा आकार एवं वजन बहुत कम</span></p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo3;\\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\"><span style=\\"mso-list: Ignore;\\">&middot;<span style=\\"font: 7.0pt \\\'Times New Roman\\\';\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">अधिक विश्&zwj;वसनीय</span></p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo3;\\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\"><span style=\\"mso-list: Ignore;\\">&middot;<span style=\\"font: 7.0pt \\\'Times New Roman\\\';\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">पोर्टेबल एवं आसान रख-रखाव</span></p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo3;\\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\"><span style=\\"mso-list: Ignore;\\">&middot;<span style=\\"font: 7.0pt \\\'Times New Roman\\\';\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">उच्&zwj;चस्&zwj;तरीय भाषाओं का बृहद् स्&zwj;तर पर प्रयोग </span></p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\\"><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 8.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"MsoNormal\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\\"><strong><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; color: #4f81bd; mso-themecolor: accent1; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">कम्&zwj;प्&zwj;यूटरों की चर्तुथ पीढ़ी (</span></strong><strong><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; color: #4f81bd; mso-themecolor: accent1; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">1971-1980</span></strong><strong><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; color: #4f81bd; mso-themecolor: accent1; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">) :-</span></strong></p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"MsoNormal\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\\"><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\"><span style=\\"mso-tab-count: 1;\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>सन् </span><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">1980 </span><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">से लेकर आज तक के कम्&zwj;प्&zwj;यूटरों को चर्तुथ पीढ़ी के कम्&zwj;प्&zwj;यूटरों की श्रेणी में रखा गया है। इस पीढ़ी में आई</span><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">.</span><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">सी.</span><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">, &lsquo;</span><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">इन्&zwj;ट्रीग्रेटेड सर्किट</span><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">&rsquo; </span><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">का प्रयोग किया गया है। जिसे </span><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">&lsquo;</span><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">लार्ज इन्&zwj;ट्रीग्रेटेड सर्किट</span><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">&rsquo; vlsi &lsquo;</span><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\';\\">वेरी लार्ज </span><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">इन्&zwj;ट्रीग्रेटेड सर्किट</span><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">&rsquo; </span><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">भी कहा जाता है। इसमें लगभग तीन लाख ट्रान्जिस्&zwj;टरो के बराबर आई</span><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">.</span><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">सी एक इंच के चौथाई भाग में शामिल हो सकता है। आई</span><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">.</span><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">सी के अविष्&zwj;कार से पूरी सी</span><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">.</span><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">पी.यू. यूनिट एक छोटी सी चिप में आ गई जिसे माइक्रो प्रोसेसर कहा जाता है। आई</span><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">.</span><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">सी का प्रयोग करने वाले कम्&zwj;प्&zwj;यूटरों को माइक्रो कम्&zwj;प्&zwj;यूटर कहा गया। सबसे पहला माइक्रो कम्&zwj;प्&zwj;यूटर अल्&zwj;टेयर </span><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">8800 </span><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">माइक्रो कम्&zwj;प्&zwj;यूटर था जिसे मिट्स नामक कंपनी ने बनाया है। बिल गेट्स को कम्&zwj;प्&zwj;यूटर का स्&zwj;वामी कहा जाता है। </span></p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"MsoNormal\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\\"><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 8.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"MsoNormal\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\\"><strong><u><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; color: #4f81bd; mso-themecolor: accent1; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">चतुर्थ पीढ़ी कम्&zwj;प्&zwj;यूटरो के लक्षण</span></u></strong><strong><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; color: #4f81bd; mso-themecolor: accent1; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\"> &ndash; </span></strong></p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo4;\\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\"><span style=\\"mso-list: Ignore;\\">&middot;<span style=\\"font: 7.0pt \\\'Times New Roman\\\';\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">वेरी लार्ज स्&zwj;केल इन्&zwj;ट्रीग्रेशन तकनीक का उपयोग</span></p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo4;\\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\"><span style=\\"mso-list: Ignore;\\">&middot;<span style=\\"font: 7.0pt \\\'Times New Roman\\\';\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">आकार में अदभुत कमी </span></p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo4;\\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\"><span style=\\"mso-list: Ignore;\\">&middot;<span style=\\"font: 7.0pt \\\'Times New Roman\\\';\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">साधारण आदमी की क्रय-क्षमता के अंदर</span></p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo4;\\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\"><span style=\\"mso-list: Ignore;\\">&middot;<span style=\\"font: 7.0pt \\\'Times New Roman\\\';\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">अधिक प्रभावशाली</span><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">,</span><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\"> विश्&zwj;वसनीय एवं अद्भुत गतिमान</span></p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo4;\\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\"><span style=\\"mso-list: Ignore;\\">&middot;<span style=\\"font: 7.0pt \\\'Times New Roman\\\';\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">अधिक मेमोरी क्षमता</span></p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo4;\\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\"><span style=\\"mso-list: Ignore;\\">&middot;<span style=\\"font: 7.0pt \\\'Times New Roman\\\';\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">कम्&zwj;प्&zwj;यूटरों के विभिन्&zwj;न नेटवर्क का विकास</span></p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"MsoNormal\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\\"><strong><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 8.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"MsoNormal\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\\"><strong><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; color: #4f81bd; mso-themecolor: accent1; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">कम्&zwj;प्&zwj;यूटरों की पंचम पीढ़ी (</span></strong><strong><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; color: #4f81bd; mso-themecolor: accent1; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">1980 </span></strong><strong><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; color: #4f81bd; mso-themecolor: accent1; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">से अब तक) :-</span></strong></p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"MsoNormal\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: .5in; line-height: normal;\\"><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">कम्&zwj;प्&zwj;यूटरों की पाचवी पीढ़ी में वर्तमान के शक्तिशाली एवं उच्&zwj;च तकनीक वाले कम्&zwj;प्&zwj;यूटर से लेकर भविष्&zwj;य में आने वाले कम्&zwj;प्&zwj;यूटरो को शामिल किया गया है। इस पीढ़ी के कम्&zwj;प्&zwj;यूटरों में आर्टीफीशियल इन्&zwj;ट्रलेजिन्&zwj;स का प्रयोग किया गया है । चर्तुथ जनरेशन के कम्&zwj;प्&zwj;यूटर में उपयोग होने वाले माइक्रो प्रोसेसर में सबसे पहले </span><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">1970 </span><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">में इन्&zwj;टेल </span><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">4004 </span><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">का निर्माण हुआ जिसे मार्सियन हाफ ने इन्&zwj;टेल कार्पोरेशन की मदद से किया था। इस पीढ़ी के प्रारंभ में कम्&zwj;प्&zwj;यूटरों को परस्&zwj;पर संयोजित किया गया ताकि डाटा तथा सूचना की आपस में साझेदारी तथा आदान प्रदान हो सके। नए आई.सी. सर्किट-अर्ल्&zwj;टालार्ज <span style=\\"mso-spacerun: yes;\\">&nbsp;</span>स्&zwj;केल इन्&zwj;ट्रीग्रेटेड सर्किट ने पुराने इन्&zwj;ट्रीग्रेटेड सर्किट वेरी लार्ज स्&zwj;केल सर्किट को शुरू किया गया। इस पीढ़ी में प्रतिदिन कम्&zwj;प्&zwj;यूटर के आकार को घटाने का प्रयास किया जा रहा है।</span></p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"MsoNormal\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: .5in; line-height: normal;\\"><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 7.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">&nbsp;</span></p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"MsoNormal\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\\"><strong><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; color: #4f81bd; mso-themecolor: accent1; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">पंचम पीढ़ी के लक्षण :-</span></strong></p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo5;\\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\"><span style=\\"mso-list: Ignore;\\">१-<span style=\\"font: 7.0pt \\\'Times New Roman\\\';\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">कम्&zwj;प्&zwj;यूटर के विभिन्&zwj;न आकार</span></p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo5;\\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\"><span style=\\"mso-list: Ignore;\\">२-<span style=\\"font: 7.0pt \\\'Times New Roman\\\';\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">इंटरनेट </span></p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo5;\\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\"><span style=\\"mso-list: Ignore;\\">३-<span style=\\"font: 7.0pt \\\'Times New Roman\\\';\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\\">मल्&zwj;टीमीडिया </span></p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo5;\\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\\"HI\\" style=\\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \\\'Karma Regular\\\'; mso-ansi-language: E